Equinox Desktop Client Source Code Documentation

Packages 
Package Description
equinox
This package contains all classes of the application.
equinox.controller
This package contains controller classes.
equinox.css
This package contains css files.
equinox.data
This package contains data classes.
equinox.data.fileType
This package contains file types.
equinox.data.input
This package contains process input objects.
equinox.data.material
This package contains all material classes.
equinox.data.ui
This package contains user interface data objects.
equinox.font
This package contains iconic font classes.
equinox.fxml
This package contains all FXML resources for the default 'steelblue' color theme.
equinox.image
This package contains image resources.
equinox.network
This package contains network classes.
equinox.plugin
This package contains plugin interfaces.
equinox.process
This package cotains all process classes.
equinox.task
This package contains task classes.
equinox.task.serializableTask
This package contains the serializable form of savable tasks.
equinox.utility
This package contains utility classes.
equinox.utility.exception
This package contains exception classes.
equinox.viewer
This package contains 3D viewer classes.
